@H3CDataEngine hello, the JIRA referenced in the title (NIFI-6510) is not related to ListHDFS, is there another JIRA?

Also, I believe the issue you are experiencing has already been fixed on master and will be in the next 1.10.0 release:

https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NIFI-6339

I've removed the `.travis.yml` changes from this PR.

@alopresto @thenatog Once you review and are a +1 on this PR, based on the other +1s already received, the PR can be merged.

The JIRA for adding a Java 11 build to Travis CI is [NIFI-5505](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NIFI-5505).

@pvillard31 - 

I've rebased to master and updated the code.  Please let me know if you have any additional advice.

Thanks
